                    <p class="govuk-body">the Department has reasonable grounds to suspect fraud, financial irregularity, dishonesty or negligence by the Employer or the Training Provider in connection with this Agreement;</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="govuk-!-margin-left-8">
                <div class="clause-column-fig">
                    <h4 class="govuk-body">14.1.3.</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="clause-column-content govuk-!-margin-left-3">
                    <p class="govuk-body">any employee or other individual carrying out activities on behalf of the Employer or a Connected Employer has (a) acted dishonestly or negligently at any time in connection with this Agreement or (b) taken any actions which, in the reasonable opinion of the Department, bring or are likely to bring the Department's name, brand or reputation or the Apprenticeships brand into disrepute;</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="govuk-!-margin-left-8">
                <div class="clause-column-fig">
                    <h4 class="govuk-body">14.1.4.</h4>
                </div>
